result.name: Choi Wan Hin Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text: Haven’t been here for a while. Used to come with Gramps and Dai Bak Leung for after lunch dim sum. Average across the board. Good attentive service for Grandma’s birthday dinner.
Good place to have Dim Sum for lunch. Reasonable price and taste good.
Excellent dim sum. A lot of choices. We had family gathering there and we enjoyed the gathering time while having good food
Not even one star value. Very bad attitude and no english menu. I wonder how they run this place in the building where many expats work.
Staff in dirty uniform, with casual personal hygiene. Carpet, toilet and in unsanitary condition. Went there afternoon tea time, food quality very disappointing.

result.adr_address: 香港鰂魚涌英皇道979號
result.name: 彩雲軒海鮮酒家

reviews.text:
好撚垃圾 打電話訂定冬瓜盅同片皮鴨
講就話有但去到乜撚都冇 
個部長仲要講到係我地錯咁
屌你 連門口個呀姐都知我地訂左果兩邊野
佢都仲可以大大聲屌我地話我地整係訂左半隻鵝？？？
問佢野又唔撚應 講多兩句仲走撚左去😡😡
垃圾酒樓 😡😡😡永久black list🖕🏻🖕🏻🖕🏻

侍應態度不太好還會一直裝忙
客人等了很久也裝作沒看到
但我看到有人給小費他們會特別熱心
食物也從剛開幕的好吃到現在的不太好吃
待應工作散慢，問關於冲茶問題，話唔關我事，但對熟客招呼週到(大冢明喇)。😱😰
蒜香牛柳粒，蒜片香脆，牛柳粒滑煎到剛剛好，
普通一家粤式飲茶酒樓，食物味道一般，服務員太少了，部長欠笑容，要自助斟茶。
